# Unit Test Cases for Contact & Account Plugins

## ✅ Contact Plugin: Prevent Duplicate Emails
- Create a Contact with **email@example.com**.
- Try creating another Contact with **email@example.com**.
- ❌ Expected: "A contact with this email address already exists."

## ✅ Account Plugin: Auto-Create Contact
- Create a new Account with name **XYZ Corp**.
- Expected: A Contact is automatically created with:
  - First Name: Default
  - Last Name: XYZ Corp
- ✅ Check that the Contact is linked to the Account.
